tf.InteractiveSession()
for dims in range(1, 4):
    shape = [2] + [4] * dims + [3]
    x_np = np.random.randn(*shape) + 1.0j * np.random.randn(*shape)
    x_np = x_np.astype(np.complex64)
    x_tf = tf.constant(x_np, tf.complex64)
    k_np = fft(x_np)
    k_tf = fft(x_tf)
    self.assertLess(max(abs(k_np - k_tf.eval())), 0.001)
    x_np = ifft(k_np)
    x_tf = ifft(k_tf)
    self.assertLess(max(abs(x_np - x_tf.eval())), 0.001)
